# Claude Code baseline — transient state and per-session artifacts.
# Everything listed here is regenerated by hooks/skills/runs; never staged.

# Per-run state (workflow tracker, consent tokens, swarm plans, last test verdict, harness logs)
.claude/state/

# Per-session signal collection. `memory_stop` hook auto-extracts memory
# candidates here every turn; `/memory-flush` curates keepers into the
# canonical six (landmarks/libraries/decisions/landmines/conventions/
# pending-questions) and resets the body. The file's only durable shape
# is in src/memory/_pending.template.md (the pristine ship-time placeholder
# overlaid by scripts/build-template.sh stage 2). The live file is pure
# session noise — never staged.
.claude/memory/_pending.md
.claude/memory/_pending.md.body

# Cross-session continuity snapshot (PreCompact + Stop hooks write,
# SessionStart hook reads). Pure session state, not project knowledge.
.claude/memory/_resume.md

# Legacy agent-memory directories (subagents removed in 2026-04-27 refactor;
# any stragglers from prior sessions should not be committed)
.claude/agent-memory/

# Per-skill working memory not part of the canonical six-file system
.claude/skill-memory/

# Init-project run logs
.claude/state/init/

# Backed-up seed snapshots produced by /init-project §16 re-runs
docs/init/seed.*.md
!docs/init/seed.md

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor noise
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# npm package
node_modules/

# Intermediate build outputs. Everything generated by the build pipeline goes
# under obj/ so the repo root stays clean of artifacts. Contents:
#   obj/template/  — the npm-shipped baseline tree (scripts/build-template.sh)
#   obj/site/      — the eleventy-rendered docs site (`npm run build:site`)
obj/

# Logs
*.log

# Playwright MCP local profile (.mcp.json pins --user-data-dir here so the
# MCP never touches a system browser profile and cannot collide with the
# user's daily Firefox/Chrome on macOS LaunchServices).
.playwright-mcp/

# npm pack tarballs
create-baseline-*.tgz

# Local-only safety archives produced when migrating site infrastructure.
# Kept on disk for rollback; never committed.
_archive*/

# Generated PlantUML renders — /spec-render regenerates on demand from
# the .md spec source of truth. Keep .md tracked; render byproducts not.
docs/specs/*.rendered/

# OS noise
**/.DS_Store

# Claude Code's project-local config directory. Holds session transcripts
# (.config/projects/*.jsonl) which can record credentials the model has seen,
# plus per-plugin configuration. Never staged. Workstation hygiene scan
# (runbook Sweep #2) is the operator's responsibility.
.config/

# PlantUML vendored binary — side-fetched at install time, ~19 MB, not part
# of the published baseline (rsync-excluded in scripts/build-template.sh
# and missing from package.json `files`). Recoverable from the upstream
# release, not source-controlled.
.claude/bin/plantuml.jar

# Python bytecode caches (the harness's lifecycle hooks invoke python3
# inline for resume-snapshot writing; CPython drops .pyc files next to the
# source on import). Never staged.
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# code-browser skill: per-repo cache + conventions files written by the
# helpers. The .gitignore that used to live alongside the skill files was
# dropped by npm pack (npm's default behavior on nested .gitignore), so
# the patterns live here at the repo root instead.
.claude/skills/code-browser/cache/
.claude/skills/code-browser/conventions.json
.claude/skills/code-browser/conventions.md
